metadata.name: Sakura Project #1
metadata.description: 5678 anime inspired NFTs. Explore the world of Inferen as two warring factions compete to find The Great Bloom. Will they use the power of The Great Bloom to save humanity or to control it? Join the fight as we create a community led, branching narrative and set a new standard for NFTs with a first-of-its-kind, transferrable licensing agreement for holders.
